    <title>Assisted Transportation & Engagement | Let’s Car’raoke</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Care-forward transportation designed for riders who need extra time, patience, and support. A premium service for structured trips, programs, and appointments."
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="header">
      <div class="container header-inner">
        <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="Home">
          <img
            src="/assets/lets-carraoke.png"
            alt="Let’s Car’raoke logo"
            loading="eager"
            width="200"
            height="100"
          />
        </a>

        <nav class="main-nav" aria-label="Primary">
          <a class="nav-link" href="/services">Services</a>
          <a class="nav-link" href="/pricing">Pricing</a>
          <a class="nav-link" href="/#contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="page">
      <h1>Assisted Transportation & Engagement</h1>
      <p><strong>Care-forward rides for guests who need extra support and patience.</strong></p>

      <p>
        This service is designed for riders who require more than a standard pickup and drop-off.
        That may include calmer pacing, additional time, assistance getting to and from the vehicle,
        and a more supportive ride environment for school, appointments, programs, or structured outings.
      </p>

      <p>
        This is a premium service because it requires additional care, responsibility, and attention
        from our drivers to ensure a safe, respectful, and reliable experience.
      </p>

      <h2>What’s included</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Extra time and flexible pacing</li>
        <li>Calm, supportive ride environment</li>
        <li>Assistance as appropriate to the booking</li>
        <li>Reliability for structured or scheduled trips</li>
        <li>Clear service guidelines and expectations</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        <a class="btn" href="/pricing">View pricing and booking options</a>
      </p>
    </main>

